      "side": 1,
      "message": "(assuming this is claude) I\u0027ve noticed claude doing this as well - referring to past stuff that\u0027s no longer valid. I don\u0027t exactly know what our preference is as a whole, but I personally prefer that we phrase things as they are today, rather than requiring understanding of issues from the past, since fixed. So I would prefer this to be rephrased to document the correct current behaviour only.",
      "revId": "4d0b410a3bd1921749552ee640b8ba07fb3020f2",
      "serverId": "d5d70762-12d0-45a1-890d-524b12d3f735"
    },
    {
